	<Title>新疆塔里木沙漠伴行路发生特大交通事故4死2伤</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2007-9-10</ReportTime>
	
        <Content> <Paragraph><Sentence>
       <Event eid="e1" type="thoughtevent"> <Participant sid="s1">新华网</Participant><Title type="relTime" tid="t1">9月10日</Title><Denoter type="statement" did="d1">电</Denoter></Event>
        </Sentence>
    <Sentence><Event eid="e2"><Time type="relTime" tid="t2">9月10日6时许</Time>，<Location lid="l2">塔里木沙漠公路伴行路</Location>发生起一起特大路外<Denoter type="emergency" did="d2">交通事故</Denoter></Event>，
    <Event eid="e3"><Object sid="s3">一辆小轿车</Object>与<Object sid="s3">一辆小客车</Object><Denoter type="operation" did="d3">相撞</Denoter></Event>，
    造成<Event eid="e4"><Participant sid="s4">4人</Participant>当场<Denoter type="stateChange" did="d4">死亡</Denoter></Event>，
    <Event eid="e5"><Participant sid="s5">2名司机</Participant><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d5">受伤</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e6" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s6">记者</Participant>从<Participant oid="o6">新疆公安厅交警部门</Participant><Denoter type="perception" did="d6">了解</Denoter>到</Event>，发生事故的两辆车均属和田地区，<Event eid="e7"><Time type="relTime" tid="t7">10日上午</Time>，一辆车号为新Ｒ―18611的<Object sid="s7">小轿车</Object>行驶到<Location lid="l7">塔里木油田轮南镇至库尔勒市管道检修伴行公路72公里</Location>处时，与一辆车号为新Ｒ―20777的<Object sid="s7">小客车</Object><Denoter type="action" did="d7">相撞</Denoter></Event>，
                造成小轿车车内<Event eid="e8"><Participant sid="s8">4名女性</Participant>当场<Denoter type="stateChange" did="d8">死亡</Denoter></Event>，
                <Event eid="e9"><Participant sid="s9">两车司机</Participant><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d9">受伤</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
		<Paragraph><Sentence>据了解，发生事故的路段位于新疆巴音郭楞蒙古自治州境内的轮南镇至库尔勒市之间，属封闭道路，主要是塔里木油田检修油气管道的伴行公路，禁止社会车辆通行。</Sentence></Paragraph>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e10"><Denoter type="emergency" did="d10">事故</Denoter>发生</Event>后，<Event eid="e11">巴音郭楞蒙古自治州党委、人民政府迅速派出由公安、安监等部门组成的<Participant sid="s11，s12，s14">工作组</Participant><Denoter type="movement" did="d11">赶赴</Denoter><Location type="destination" lid="l11">现场</Location></Event>，<Event eid="e12"><Time type="relTime"  tid="t12">立即</Time>将<Participant oid="o12">受伤人员</Participant><Denoter type="movement" did="d12">送往</Denoter><Location type="destination" lid="l12">医院</Location></Event>
                <Event eid="e13"><Denoter type="operation" did="d13">救治</Denoter></Event>，
                <Event eid="e14">并<Denoter type="operation" did="d14">开展</Denoter>道路疏通、死者身份调查和善后处理等<Object oid="o14">工作</Object></Event>。</Sentence>
                <Sentence><Event eid="e15"><Time type="relTime" tid="t15">目前</Time>，<Object oid="o15">事故原因</Object>正在<Denoter type="operation" did="d15">调查</Denoter>中</Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
	</Content>
